<abstract audience="internal" id="aspace_001">The COVID-19 Scientific Response in India Collection documents research, laboratory work, public health communication, and outreach activities undertaken during the COVID-19 pandemic between 2020 and 2021. The collection includes press releases, laboratory records, vaccination awareness materials, and photographs documenting institutional and community responses.</abstract>
<abstract audience="internal" id="aspace_002">The collection contains digital records related to COVID-19 research and response efforts in India. Materials include institutional communications, laboratory documentation, public outreach posters, and photographs of research and community activities.</abstract>
